Package: NPdata
Type: Package
Title: Functions to Automate Downloading Financial and Economic Data Available
  Through Different Official Government of Nepal Websites
Version: 0.0.1
Date: 2015-07-10
Authors@R:
  person(given=c("Nayan","Krishna"), family="Joshi",
  email="nayankrishnajoshi@gmail.com", role=c("aut","cre"))
Description: Functions to automate downloading financial and economic data
  available through different official Government of Nepal different official
  Government of Nepal (GoN) websites. Currently, the package allows you to
  download stock market data (real time stock quotes, daily historical stock
  prices and volumes, daily historical indexes, and daily historical floor
  sheets) from Nepal Stock Exchange (NEPSE) and daily historical foreign
  exchange rates from Nepal Rastra Bank.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.2.1),
    xml2,
    httr,
    rvest,
    curl
Imports:
    xml2 (>= 0.1.1),
    httr (>= 1.0.0),
    rvest (>= 0.2.0.9000),
    curl (>= 0.9),
    xts (>= 0.9.7),
    dygraphs (>= 0.4.5),
    data.table (>= 1.9.4),
    quantmod (>= 0.4.4)
Suggests:
